^fbcode/eden/mononoke(?!/public_autocargo).*/Cargo\.toml$
# strip other scm code  unrelated to mononoke to prevent triggering unnecessary checks
^fbcode/eden/(?!mononoke|/scm/lib/xdiff.*)/.*$
